WEBVTT

00:02:00.402 --> 00:02:04.438
The reality is that civil society,
journalists and activists

00:02:04.462 --> 00:02:09.291
are coming under attack
from extremist groups on the one hand,

00:02:09.315 --> 00:02:11.045
and, in many countries,

00:02:11.069 --> 00:02:13.504
also from their own governments.

00:02:13.528 --> 00:02:16.920
We're seeing bloggers
and journalists being jailed,

00:02:16.944 --> 00:02:18.382
charged and intimidated

00:02:18.406 --> 00:02:19.924
by their own governments,

00:02:19.948 --> 00:02:23.343
many of which are allies
with the West in the war on terror.

00:02:23.785 --> 00:02:25.422
Just three examples.

00:02:25.446 --> 00:02:27.302
A friend and former colleague of mine,

00:02:27.326 --> 00:02:28.558
Hisham Almiraat,

00:02:28.582 --> 00:02:31.626
has been charged
with threatening state security,